  "text": "每个人都有盲区\n说出来别人反驳才知道哪里有问题\n不说永远都在自己的边界里\n所以说错了其实也没啥\n\n别人问的不懂的尽量多听少说\n不在能力圈的尽量不重仓\n别人买的大涨大跌看不懂的不给买卖建议\n万一耽误了别人发财也不好\nQuote\nkking2020\n@Btc_kking\nI used to think Lü Xiaotong still had some real chops\nWatched one of his clips yesterday\nHe kept hinting that this AI wave is just another bubble—fine, whatever\nBut when he said even Haili Shi doesn't dare to expand production, I straight-up lost it laughing\n\nSure\n7:01 PM · Jun 4, 2026",
